  "text": "Despite the existence of clinical studies on LVAD implantation [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , no guidelines for the myocardial suture based on a numerical model could be found. The work presented by presented by Charitos and Sievers (2010) on a modified technique for LVAD implantation is a good example of what is usually found in the literature. As they present their methodology, they do not elaborate on the minimum spacing of 2.5 mm between two pledgeted U-suture that they recommend. Nevertheless, our numerical threshold is in good agreement with the LVAD implantation technique presented in their study.",
